reviewText: It's a good movie I like it good acting as well

Lots better then expected for a shark movie.

D~
The dialogue is awful, the plot is cliche, but considering it is another shark movie...well it could have been worse. I mostly watched it for Jo from Eureka (Erica Cerra).

this was a a horrible movie with the word Shark attached to the title and there was very little shark footage...This movie wasn't funny or action packed...the acting was bad and nothing interesting about the plot to speak of...Stay away save your 90 minutes for a better watch..
This is a great sci-fi movie to watch I love it
Most of the movie was good - good action and story. Ending was a let down.
Not much shark footage, but good movie to watch.
